```{r pancreas 32289276, include=FALSE}

PMID_32289276 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32289276', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32289276 <- paste0(PMID_32289276$journal,' ', PMID_32289276$year, ' ', PMID_32289276$month,';', PMID_32289276$volume,'(', PMID_32289276$number,'):', PMID_32289276$pages)

PubMed_32289276 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32289276$eprint)

doi_32289276 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32289276$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)
```
